{"tid":1280051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"極邪惡 藍絲竟然勾結外國勢力禍害香港","createTime":"2019-07-03T00:07:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T08:22:34.000Z","uid":172093,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dd3dc152bb29d8d9c21c76c49598e917ab8c058f","tid":1280051,"uid":172093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T00:07:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BP2JEAX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBP2JEAX.png&h=7a3262c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拿 係以上圖片可以見到呢個出賣義士既tg channel <br />\n佢琴日就鬼拍後尾枕咁彈左句十幾位同事<br />\n好有可能係一間媒體公司或者it公司營運既<br />\n証明好可能係藍絲或者政府請返黎整造白色恐怖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f0GitvG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff0GitvG.png&h=6b6437fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n到第二張啦 由於小弟用緊係香港時間<br />\n當時三點幾 我亦訓左<br />\n個channel又鬼拍後尾枕啦 出左句佢地個邊係五點幾<br />\n咁即係快香港兩個鐘或者慢十個鐘<br />\n就咁睇 有d似澳洲<br />\n不過點都好 證明間公司係外國<br />\n原來真係有人勾結外國勢力 不過係藍絲 係政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7883bfe6d4bf18abd47503812523f0e3a05609ee","tid":1280051,"uid":172093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T00:10:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5b2c0dc133948e99a3ba987dff744d37d8efd31a","tid":1280051,"uid":172093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T00:14:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8aef9f5628285a306b1ce9388800c307ef6f6eaf","tid":1280051,"uid":172093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T00:18:09.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ab6da8e930fd393a45e30728a956268e82a8465a","tid":1280051,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T00:21:06.000Z","msg":"政府公然勾結外國勢力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n居然俾走資派滲透政府內部<br />\n違反我地毛主席既意志<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec9b57fe1b4c1652f39a35